  "operation_name": "aclnnApplyTopKTopP",
  "description": "接口功能：对原始输入logits进行top-k和top-p采样过滤。\n\n计算公式：\n对输入logits按最后一轴进行升序排序，得到对应的排序结果sortedValue和sortedIndices。\nsortedValue, sortedIndices = sort(logits, dim=-1, descending=false, stable=true)\n\n计算保留的阈值（第k大的值）。\ntopKValue[b][v] = sortedValue[b][sortedValue.size(1) - k[b]]\n\n生成top-k需要过滤的mask。\ntopKMask = sortedValue < topKValue\n\n通过topKMask将小于阈值的部分置为-Inf。\nsortedValue[b][v] = -Inf，当 topKMask[b][v]=true；sortedValue[b][v] = sortedValue[b][v]，当 topKMask[b][v]=false。\n\n通过softmax将经过top-k过滤后的数据按最后一轴转换为概率分布。\nprobsValue = softmax(sortedValue, dim=-1)\n\n按最后一轴计算累计概率（从最小的概率开始累加）。\nprobsSum = cumsum(probsValue, dim=-1)\n\n生成top-p的mask，累计概率小于等于1-p的位置需要过滤掉，并保证每个batch至少保留一个元素。\ntopPMask[b][v] = probsSum[b][v] <= 1-p[b]\ntopPMask[b][-1] = false\n\n通过topPMask将小于阈值的部分置为-Inf。\nsortedValue[b][v] = -Inf，当 topPMask[b][v]=true；sortedValue[b][v] = sortedValue[b][v]，当 topPMask[b][v]=false。\n\n将过滤后的结果按sortedIndices还原到原始顺序。\nout[b][v] = sortedValue[b][sortedIndices[b][v]]\n\n其中0 <= b < logits.size(0), 0 <= v < logits.size(1)。",
  "api_flow": "two-step",
  "inter_parameter_constraints": [
    {
      "type": "presence_dependency",
      "params": [
        "p",
        "k"
      ],
      "expr": "not ((p is None) and (k is None))",
      "description": "参数p和k不能同时为空，至少需要提供其中一个。",
      "source": null,
      "target": null
    },
    {
      "type": "type_equality",
      "params": [
        "logits",
        "p",
        "out"
      ],
      "expr": "logits.dtype == out.dtype and ((p is None) or (logits.dtype == p.dtype))",
      "description": "out的数据类型必须与logits一致；如果提供p，则p的数据类型也必须与logits一致。",
      "source": null,
      "target": null
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_equality",
      "params": [
        "logits",
        "out"
      ],
      "expr": "logits.shape == out.shape",
      "description": "out的shape必须与logits完全相同。",
      "source": null,
      "target": null
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_value_dependency",
      "params": [
        "logits",
        "p"
      ],
      "expr": "(p is None) or (p.shape[0] == logits.shape[0])",
      "description": "如果提供p，则p的长度必须等于logits的第0维大小。",
      "source": "logits",
      "target": [
        "p"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "shape_value_dependency",
      "params": [
        "logits",
        "k"
      ],
      "expr": "(k is None) or (k.shape[0] == logits.shape[0])",
      "description": "如果提供k，则k的长度必须等于logits的第0维大小。",
      "source": "logits",
      "target": [
        "k"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "value_dependency",
      "params": [
        "logits",
        "k"
      ],
      "expr": "(k is None) or (max(k) <= logits.shape[1])",
      "description": "如果提供k，则k中的最大值必须小于等于logits的第1维大小。",
      "source": "logits",
      "target": [
        "k"
      ]
    }
  ],
